    R1 -->|needs| F1
    R2 -->|needs| F2

    %% Fulfillments can be met by ANY qualification
    F1 -->|qualified by| Q3
    F1 -->|qualified by| F3
    F2 -->|qualified by| Q4
    
    %% Monk flurry must go through intermediate fulfillment
    F3 -->|qualified by| Q1
    F3 -->|qualified by| Q2

